<h2 id=3D"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-8f1f2647" class=3D"wp-=
block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-=
heading-8f1f2647">The Knitulator</h2>



<p class=3D"has-ti-fg-alt-color has-text-color">The Knitulator is a handy a=
nd fast way to calculate how to increase or decrease a certain number of st=
itches evenly throughout a row of knitting. </p>



<p class=3D"has-ti-fg-alt-color has-text-color">If you=E2=80=99ve ever been=
 stumped by a knitting instruction that reads something like =E2=80=98incre=
ase x number of stitches evenly throughout row=E2=80=99, simply plug in you=
r starting stitch count, the number of stitches you wish to increase or dec=
rease by, and hit the =E2=80=98knitulate=E2=80=99 button.</p>
</div>
</div></div>




<div class=3D"knitulator">
<form id=3D"frm1">Please help me to &nbsp;<input id=3D"incdecinc" checked=
