itches" style=3D"width: 90px; height:38px; text-align: center;" type=3D"tex=
t" value=3D"20"> stitches <br> to give <span id=3D"calcTot">120</span> stit=
ches total.

</form><br>
<a class=3D"knitulate" href=3D"https://mimicodd.com/knitulator-increase-dec=
